<TestCaseEntity>
   <description>#Disappearing persoon entity
In onderzoek, when you add an entity person and attach a rol/proces to this person: if you update the rolproces by clicking directly on it in the grid, the entity disappears. 

If you first open the person record, and from there update the rol/proces, it will not disappear.
Menu, Opsporing, Onderzoek
Select any existing onderzoek. 
Click on tab Entiteiten
Click on button nieuwe entiteit
Select type entiteit 'Persoon'
Field achternaam: start typing any name and select an existing person
Select a Rol/Proces e.g. 'Aangifte/Aangever'
Fill mandatory fields on main accordeon: toevoegen als slachtoffer- NEE, Slachtofferhulp- NEE
Click on accordion Reden Aangifte and add one
Click on accordion Strafbaar feit and add one
Click on Save: the rol/process is saved
Click on Save again to save the persoon
Persoon does not disappear:
Person disappears:</description>
